snippet.description:
Calmed by the Dark is a free game and can be downloaded here: https://punishedmike.itch.io/calmed-by-the-dark

Discover a  parallel dimension to ours in Calmed by the Dark, a dimension filled with mysteries, monsters and survivors. Learn how to master your unimaginable powers and join a group that will shape the destiny of the future.

Gameplay Mechanics:

*RPG Elements ( i.e. upgrading your character health, damage, armor stats and more.);
*Choices: Some choices affect story, gameplay and characters;
*City Adminstration: Recruit members, buy buildings and manage your army.
*Combat: Test your strategy using dash, special attacks, fast attacks and strong attacks in a dynamic combat system;
*Time Cycle: Some events will only happen at some specific time;
*Become a Legend: Use your powers to decide the fate of everyone or maybe don't and just see what happens.
*Date: Find a special one and take her to a cinema, restaurant, see the sky or maybe go to a bar.
*World: Play in world filled with dangers, people, collectionables and secrets.

